y suggests that "giving a man a fish" might ultimately be more revolutionary than "teaching a man to fish."  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 21. Jun 2021) 0aArab Spring, 2010-xSocial aspects. 0aCharitieszEgypt. 0aCharityxReligious aspectsxIslam. 0aIslamxCharities. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Anthropology / General.2bisacsh  a2011.  aacts of charity.  aalmsgiving.  acall for social justice.  acharity.  adeeply selfish.  aegyptian history.  aegyptian uprising.  aethnography.  afood.  agive a man a fish.  agiving to god.  agiving to the poor.  aislam.  ameal distribution.  amiddle eastern history.  anon compassionate ethics.  apious volunteers.  apost revolutionary egypt.  asufi soup kitchen.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019 Englishz978311061076508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019z9783110664232oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Economics, Law & Social Sciences 2019 ENGz978311061013008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Social Sciences 2019z9783110606485oZDB-23-DSW08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUCA Complete eBook-Package 2019z978311065207908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of California Press Complete eBook-Package 2019z978311066763940uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/9780520972056zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520972056423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780520972056.jpg  a978-3-11-061013-0  EBOOK PACKAGE Economics, Law & Social Sciences 2019 ENGb2019  a978-3-11-061076-5  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019 Englishb2019  a978-3-11-065207-9  UCA Complete eBook-Package 2019b2019  a978-3-11-066763-9  University of California Press Comp